channel.description:
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/QAW6fFX.gif[/img][/center]
[u][b]Why Prodigy-X?[/b][/u]
We believe runescape private servers come down to two things - the community - and quality content. We are proud to say we have been in the runescape private server business for over 3 years and we do not plan on stopping any time soon. Prodigy-X has a lot to offer, something for everyone, but we LOVE to show off our community, from the active and helpful staff team - to the player base, everyone here is willing to help you.
[u][b]Helpful Links:[/b][/u]
[url=http://www.prodigy-x.com/forums][img]http://i44.tinypic.com/9j41t1.jpg[/img] Prodigy-X - Forums[/url] [url=http://www.prodigy-x.com/webclient][img]http://i40.tinypic.com/70xs2a.png[/img] Prodigy-X - Webclient[/url] [url=http://www.prodigy-x.com/Client.jar][img]http://i40.tinypic.com/70xs2a.png[/img] Prodigy-X - Desktop Client[/url] [url=http://prodigyxrsps.no-ip.org/vote][img]http://i.imgur.com/kjWch.gif[/img] Prodigy-X - Vote for Us[/url]
[u][b]Main attractions:[/b][/u]
- Dedicated server, 24/7 uptime, and NO LAG! - Extremely stable server, never worry about rollbacks - Daily updates & bug fixes (we mean it too!) - Stable drop rates and economy - Double XP weekends - Active and helpful staff team - Owner(s) that are active and take and implement suggestions from players - Automatic donations and voting, get your rewards instantly! - Epic donor zone in the Enchanted Valley - Highscores to see who's the best!
[u][b]Main Features:[/b][/u]
- Active Fight Pits - Duel Arena - Dominion Tower - Clan Wars (ALL maps!) - Castle Wars - Fight Caves (63 waves) - Fight Kiln (36 waves) - Barrows - King Black Dragon - Queen Black Dragon - Tormented Demons - Corporal Beast - Kalphite Queen - Nomad - Bork - Full GWD - Advanced Crystal Key Chest (3 tiers of rewards) - Detailed Slayer System (cancel tasks, co-op, points) - Summoning (Steel Titan, Pak Yak, Unicorns) - Dwarf Multicannon - Real Bandit Camp (Fast Training!) - Tzhaar City - Forinthy Dungeon (Revs, Green drags) - Brimhaven & Taverely Dungeon - Frost Dragons (Great Money!) - Glacors (REAL COMBAT!) - Vote Point Store In-Game (godswords, claws, bandos) - Donation Shop (Ranks & Items) - Money Pouch (Shop & Trade integration) - Gilded Altar (Fast Prayer XP) - New or old item looks (::itemlooks) - Quick Help (::commands or ::help) - Staff always online to help you with anything!

BUMP! We’ve just gotten moparscape sponsorship, peaked at over 80 players, growing extremely fast now. We have developed a full completionist cape, max cape, co-op slayer, 8 new bosses, and runespan minigame. Come check it out, we are unlike any other 718 - guaranteed.

item.title: Prodigy-X 718 - GROWING FAST!
item.dc:creator: @prodigyxrsps prodigyxrsps
item.description:
@prodigyxrsps wrote:

marcbob:

Happy for you guys that you have reached 50+ online, but I also don’t see anything in your advertisement thread that would make me want to play this over any other 718 server.

Thanks for the support, we are working on more unique content, like our slayer system for example, now offering co-op slayer, which I have never seen on another 718 server. We are releasing farming, as well as a new home location in the coming days. And REAL dungeoneering has been in development for quite a while now, its going to be epic.

Come check us out guys, give it a shot, we’re not like the rest of the 718’s.
